            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Leicestershire Police are on the hunt for a specific 1960 Rover P5 they say is linked to an ongoing insurance fraud investigation. Detectives are asking for help from the local classic car enthusiast community. While the supplied photos portray it as gray, it was originally beige. It’s possible the car has been restored and resprayed, so it might be a different color by now.",
